function changeimage()
{
    const ele=document.getElementById("tom");
    const newurl="data:image/png;base64,"
    ele.src=newurl;
    
}
function convertimage()
{
    const ele=document.getElementById("tom");
    const otherurl="data:image/jpeg;base64,"
    ele.src=otherurl;
    
}    
function showimage()
{
    const ele=document.getElementById("tom");
    const changedurl="data:image/png;base64," 
    ele.src=changedurl;   
}
